Wiiarmed README

Control the OWI Robotic Arm Edge (http://www.maplin.co.uk/robotic-arm-kit-with-usb-pc-interface-266257) using a wiimote.
Using various gestures to control the different joints.

Licence:

Don't really know much about open source licences but wiiuse is GPL 3+ so I'll stick with that.

Controls:

Wiimote roll: Shoulder
Wiimote pitch: Elbow
Wiimote yaw (Needs SensorBar or IR leds): Base rotation

Nunchuck pitch: Wrist

Button B: LED
BUTTON Z,C: Open Close Gripper

Building:


OSX:

Install wiiuse: https://github.com/rpavlik/wiiuse
Install libusb from mac ports.


Linux:
Should build with correct dependencies (wiiuse, libusb)

Windows:
On your own

Wiimote connection issues:

See https://github.com/rpavlik/wiiuse/blob/master/README.mkd
